metadata.name: #0001 LEGENDARY Panther XLR R DIAMOND ***** (Power 1481)
metadata.description:
# Description
This Race Team Rivals NFT Garage car is Legendary, with a rating of 1481. It works well on Tarmac surfaces.
# About
Race Team Rivals NFT Garage, is a mobile free-to-play game, which has now been enhanced with a collection of NFT cars unique to the game. Each of these NFTs will be unique and will guarantee for the owner to stand out in the game, both visually and performance wise. Clash of Race Teams NFT Garage is a collection of 2500 unique collectible and playable NFT vehicles.
This NFT collection for Clash of Race Teams is on the Ethereum network.
